This python app is based on Wordle with the main differences being
	1) the ability to set up different word sizes 
	2) no limits on how many games per day as it is a random word and not based on date as index.

>Play

Start bash or powershell for a running locally
```bash
python readword.py
```

>Options
   s) Show
   n) Set word size
   p) Play
   q) Quit

The code can be easily updated to read from a different word list.